{"tid":1734984,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"救理大最終一戰","createTime":"2019-11-18T12:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T12:50:24.000Z","uid":312966,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7bd3b57b24a4d3f7e0832f90235e1368b696befc","tid":1734984,"uid":312966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:37:01.000Z","msg":"四邊推已經唔掂，尖東欠gear L推唔入<br />\n急求四方八面兄弟一齊集合柯士甸路，推爆佢<br />\n全民攬埋一齊唔好再驚<br />\n驚就輸一世<br />\n麻煩推爆佢。<br />\n<br />\n隊式：<br />\n勇士車隊<br />\ngear L＆FA<br />\n和理非＆家長<br />\n車隊包尾"},{"pid":"4365ffd37e8f167b5bff308c45f29f22fde3778a","tid":1734984,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:37:18.000Z","msg":"點解政府要派人入去, 目的係一邊勸降, 一邊收集入面情報/證據, 例如有幾多人, 係咩位置, 物資情況等等, 我敢肯定入去既人一定有多於一種既攝錄監察儀器。之後, 等臨天光既時候就會派特種部隊強攻清場。<br />\n<br />\n要解救, 只能從超限戰既角度去諗, 唔好諗住可以用平常方法解救。<br />\n<br />\n戰術分析<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734914</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2a6b2f06c7bb31979a0faf3e4b114970f84d6d21","tid":1734984,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:37:45.000Z","msg":"點解唔將機油汽油入落氣球車d黑警？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734899</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"217510e849eb00b8aa5ddd7b88415844db4c75d0","tid":1734984,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:37:53.000Z","msg":"[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2216ba48455fe9de67503c4805b8eb375365edb0","tid":1734984,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:38:27.000Z","msg":"話唔到呢加係理大入面話走個班係鬼黎<br />\n專登引勇武出動救人大圍捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55845d1085d44a2a07d78ef384f3ec8c72f1eb7","tid":1734984,"uid":224801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"